  "description": "<div><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;\">Overview:</span></div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><div><p>1. The Dipping Nail Powders is easy to do it with a french and gradient effect.<br/>2.10 basic colors, especially for DP08, DP09 and DP03, other colors used for the first layer.<br/>3. The red color of DP10 is rose red in the container, but it is red after applying to nail. The picture is real shot without color, close to the real thing.  <br/>4. The advantages are simple and quick to apply, more durable than nail polish, and the disadvantage is that it is not easy to remove(in the same way as the nail gel)   <br/>5.Can be used on natural nails and false nails.<br/>6.Provide a fantastic natural look for your nails.<br/>7.Perfect for home use or professional use.<br/><br/>How to use :<br/>1. Prepare your nail<br/>2. Apply a thin coat of dip base<br/>3. Dip tip of the entire nail into the dish<br/>4. Brush off excess powder<br/>5. Apply a second coat of dip Base Coat<br/>6. Dip tip of a nail into the dish to achieve desired line<br/>7. Brush off excess powder<br/>8. Apply dip ACTIVATOR<br/>9. Smooth and refine the surface with a buffer  <br/>10. Apply top coat</p></div><div><br/></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;\">Specification:</span></div>Net content: 10 ml</span><br style=\"font-size: 16px;\"/><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Item: Impregnated powder</span><br style=\"font-size: 16px;\"/><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Features: Long lasting UV resistant gel</span><div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Style: Gradient French Nail</span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Color: holographic nude pink nails</span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Cure: natural drying</span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Smell: no smell</span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;\"><br/></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;\">Package Content:</span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1 x&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Nail Infiltration Powder</span><ul><li id=\"product-prop-2\"><p><img alt=\"433221\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/16367616/1636808815194.jpg\"/><img alt=\"433222\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/16367616/1636808815476.jpg\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br/></p></li></ul></div>",
